content: I'm excited to start browsing ThredUp's selection of high-end boutique dresses. I've had a good experience with a fast-fashion retailer recently, and I'm hoping to find something similar in quality and style on ThredUp, but at a lower price point. The dress I bought from the fast-fashion retailer cost $40, so I'm hoping to find something comparable on ThredUp. Do you think I could find a high-end boutique dress on ThredUp that's similar in style and quality to what I would find at my usual high-end boutique, but at a lower price point?
